      CHANGES in rexpokit VERSION 0.25

NEW FEATURES
    
    o Rewrote compiled code wrappers to imrpove performance (~10-40%).
    o Fixed Fortran flags.
    o Added demos.

OTHER CHANGES
    
    o Minor changes to documentation to avoid links outside of package (to diversitree and expoRkit)
    o Changed DESCRIPTION file to have this, reducing dependencies:
        Depends: 
        LinkingTo: Rcpp
        Imports: SparseM
    o Changed NAMESPACE file to have this, reducing dependencies:
        importFrom(SparseM, as.matrix.coo)
